high_descs: Turn to the table on your left.
Pick up the large pot on the front, right corner of the table.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator in the right corner of the kitchen, across from you.
Place the pot on the top shelf of the refrigerator, to the left of the lettuce, wait a moment for it to chill, then remove the pot from the refrigerator.
Turn around and go back to the table behind you.
Place the pot on the front left corner of the table, in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a large, cold cooking pot, on the table.

high_descs: chill and remove pot from fridge
turn to face left side of kitchen table
Turn around and face the table to the left.
Pick the pot up from the corner of the table.
Turn around and cross the room to face the fridge.
Put the pot in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and take the pot out and shut the door again.
Turn around and cross the room to face the wood table again.
Put the pot down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pot on a table.
